
Hello, and welcome to %mud_name.

This is an effort to create an opinionated fork of the LPU codebase. The goal
is to provide a more modern and feature-rich codebase for the LPMud community.

This is a work in progress. Issues may be reported at the following URL:
https://github.com/gesslar/glpu/issues

Pull requests are welcome, but are subject to the approval of the project.
